    "desc": "Personalized eCards from JibJab for every occasion. Browse, customize, send funny greeting cards online for birthdays, holidays, valentines, thank yous & more!",
    "text": "We use cookies to personalize and improve your experience. By continuing to use our website, you agree to our Cookie Policy\nOk\nSign Up\nFun Video Ecards and Greetings Starring You, Family & Friends\n0:22\nMore Online Greeting Cards to Stick Your Face In\nView More\nEcards for\nA Birthday\nCelebration\nBROWSE BIRTHDAYS\nFeatured categories\nView more\nSend Funny Ecards – All Year Long!\nThere’s always an occasion to cheer someone up - using our funny, personalized videos with JibJab style and humor. We provide 100s of Ecards and year-round fun for the whole family, your friends & co-workers. So get your smile on, and stick your face in it!\nHOLIDAYS\nValentine's Day\nEaster\nMother's Day\nIndependence Day\nThanksgiving\nHanukkah\nSt. Patrick's Day\nPassover\nFather's Day\nHalloween\nChristmas\nNew Years\nCELEBRATE\nBirthdays\nAnniversary\nWedding &\nEngagement\nGraduation\nBaby\nGREETINGS\nLove\nThanks\nYou Rock\nGet Well\nCongrats\nSorry\nBrowse All Categories\nAbout\nHelp\nTerms\nPrivacy\nJibJab®, Sendables®, Starring You® and JokeBox® are registered trademarks of JibJab Catapult CA LLC. © Copyright 1999–2023 JibJab Catapult CA LLC. All Rights Reserved.",
